column1: The  acquisition order No.  123 of 1984 (P4  pages  2A to 4A)  refers to 33  different lots which were
admittedly acquired for the Dambu lla sacred area development as reflected in P7A item 10 which
is a document relied on  by the Petitioner. The  evidence shows that development work has been
carried out on parts of the land so acquired which shows that possession has  been taken over by
